@startuml NTK-10003 Lookup Reservation Orchestration

title Unregistered Guest Self-Service Check-in\nReservation Lookup Orchestration Flow

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor "Guest" as Guest
participant "Kiosk UI" as Kiosk
participant "svc-check-in\n(Orchestrator)" as CheckIn [[/services/svc-check-in/]]
participant "svc-reservations" as Reservations [[/services/svc-reservations/]]
participant "svc-partner-\nintegrations" as Partners
participant "svc-guest-\nprofiles" as Profiles [[/services/svc-guest-profiles/]]
participant "svc-safety-\ncompliance" as Safety
participant "svc-gear-\ninventory" as Gear

== Identity Verification ==

Guest -> Kiosk : Select "Check in with\nConfirmation Code"
Kiosk -> Kiosk : Display verification form

Guest -> Kiosk : Enter last_name,\nconfirmation_code,\nadventure_date,\nparticipant_count

Kiosk -> CheckIn : [[/services/svc-check-in/ POST /check-ins/lookup-reservation]]\n{last_name, confirmation_code,\nadventure_date, participant_count,\nkiosk_device_id}

CheckIn -> CheckIn : Validate input\nNormalize confirmation_code\nCheck rate limit

== Reservation Lookup ==

CheckIn -> Reservations : [[/services/svc-reservations/ POST /reservations/search]]\n{last_name, confirmation_code,\nadventure_date, participant_count}

alt Reservation Found
    Reservations --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{reservation_id, adventure_name,\nparticipants[], booking_source}

else Reservation Not Found
    Reservations --> CheckIn : 404 Not Found

    == Partner Fallback ==

    CheckIn -> CheckIn : Extract partner prefix\nfrom confirmation_code

    alt Partner Identified (e.g., EM-, TF-, WP-)
        CheckIn -> Partners : POST /partner-integrations/verify-booking\n{partner_id, confirmation_code, last_name}

        alt Partner Confirms Booking
            Partners --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{booking_details}
        CheckIn -> Reservations : [[/services/svc-reservations/ POST /reservations]]\n(create synced reservation)
            Reservations --> CheckIn : 201 Created\n{reservation_id}

        else Partner Booking Not Found
            Partners --> CheckIn : 404 Not Found
            CheckIn --> Kiosk : 404 RESERVATION_NOT_FOUND\n"Visit service desk"
            Kiosk -> Guest : Display error message
            note right : 2-second artificial\ndelay applied
            return
        end

    else No Partner Prefix / Unknown Partner
        CheckIn --> Kiosk : 404 RESERVATION_NOT_FOUND\n"Visit service desk"
        Kiosk -> Guest : Display error message
        return
    end
end

== Guest Profile ==

CheckIn -> Profiles : [[/services/svc-guest-profiles/ GET /guest-profiles]]\n?reservation_id={id}

alt Profile Exists
    Profiles --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{guest_profile_id, profile_type}

else No Profile
    CheckIn -> Profiles : [[/services/svc-guest-profiles/ POST /guest-profiles/temporary]]\n{last_name, reservation_id}
    Profiles --> CheckIn : 201 Created\n{guest_profile_id,\nprofile_type: TEMPORARY}
end

== Parallel Status Checks ==

par Safety Compliance Check
    CheckIn -> Safety : GET /safety-compliance/waivers\n?reservation_id={id}
    Safety --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{waiver_complete, waiver_url}

else Gear Assignment Check
    CheckIn -> Gear : GET /gear-inventory/assignments\n?reservation_id={id}
    Gear --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{gear_items[], pickup_location}
end

== Session Creation ==

CheckIn -> CheckIn : Generate JWT session token\n{guest_profile_id, reservation_id,\nkiosk_device_id, expiry: 30min}
CheckIn -> CheckIn : Store session in Redis

CheckIn --> Kiosk : 200 OK\n{session_token, reservation_id,\nguest_profile_id, adventure_name,\ncheck_in_status{}, participants[]}

Kiosk -> Guest : Display check-in summary\nProceed with kiosk flow

@enduml
